<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">A decision by the Secretary denying any application for a <ref class="footnoteRef" idref="fn002578">1</ref><note type="footnote" id="fn002578"><num>1</num> So in original. Probably should be “an”.</note> obsolete ship under this chapter is final.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id78f17e18-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/92/402/s6">Pub. L. 92–402, § 6</ref>, <date date="1972-08-22">Aug. 22, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/618">86 Stat. 618</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/98/623/tII/s207/1">Pub. L. 98–623, title II, § 207(1)</ref>, <date date="1984-11-08">Nov. 8, 1984</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/98/3397">98 Stat. 3397</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
